quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  75,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  75,1,"nahi, mein qasam khata hon qayamat ke din ki"
  75,2,"aur nahi, mein qasam khata hon malamat karne walay nafs ki"
  75,3,kya ensaan yeh samajh raha hai ke hum uss ki hadion ko jama nah kar saken ge ?
  75,4,hum to is ki unglio ki poor poor taq theek bana dainay par Qadir hain
  75,5,magar ensaan chahta yeh hai ke agay bhi bad a'maliyan karta rahay
  75,6,"puchta hai"" aakhir kab aana hai woh qayamat ka din? """
  75,7,phir jab daiday pathra jayen ge
  75,8,aur chaand be noor ho jaayegaa
  75,9,aur chaand Sooraj mila kar aik kar diye jayen ge
  75,10,"uss waqt yahi ensaan kahe ga"" kahan bhaag kar jaoon? """
  75,11,"hargiz nahi, wahan koi jaye panah nah hogi"
  75,12,uss roz tairay Rab hi ke samnay ja kar tehrnahoga
  75,13,uss roz ensaan ko is ka sab agla pichla kya karaya bta diya jaye ga
  75,14,balkay ensaan khud hi apne aap ko khoob jaanta hai
  75,15,chahay woh kitni hi mawzartain paish kere
  75,16,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, iss wahi ko jaldi jaldi yaad karne ke liye apni zabaan ko harkat nah do"
  75,17,iss ko yaad kara dena aur prhhwa dena hamaray zimma hai
  75,18,lehaza jab hum isay parh rahay hon uss waqt tum iss ki qarat ko ghhor se suntay raho
  75,19,phir is ka matlab samgha dena bhi hamaray zimma hai
  75,20,"hargiz nahi, asal baat yeh hai ke tum log jaldi haasil honay wali cheez ( yani duniya ) se mohabbat rakhtay ho"
  75,21,aur akhirat ko chore dete ho
  75,22,uss roz kuch chehray tar o taaza hunge
  75,23,apne Rab ki taraf dekh rahay hunge
  75,24,aur kuch chehray udaas hon ge
  75,25,aur samajh rahay hon ge ke unn ke sath kamar toar bartao honay wala hai
  75,26,"hargiz nahi, jab jaan halaq taq poanch jaye gi"
  75,27,aur kaha jaye ga ke hai koi jhaad phoonk karne wala
  75,28,aur aadmi samajh le ga ke yeh duniya se judai ka waqt hai
  75,29,aur pindli se pindli jarr jaye gi
  75,30,woh din hoga tairay Rab ki taraf rawaangi ka
  75,31,"magar uss ne nah sach maana, aur nah namaz parhi"
  75,32,balkay jhtlaya aur palat gaya
  75,33,phir akharta howa apne ghar walon ki taraf chal diya
  75,34,yeh rawish tairay hi liye sazawar hai aur tujhi ko Zaib deti hai
  75,35,haan yeh rawish tairay hi liye sazawar hai aur tujhi ko Zaib deti hai
  75,36,kya ensaan ne yeh samajh rakha hai ke woh yuhin mehmal chore diya jaye ga ?
  75,37,kya woh aik haqeer pani ka nutfa nah tha jo ( reham madar mein ) tapkaya jata hai ?
  75,38,"phir woh aik lothra bana, phir Allah ne is ka jism banaya aur is ke aaza durust kiye"
  75,39,phir is se mard aur aurat ki do kasmain banayen
  75,40,kya woh iss par Qadir nahi hai ke marnay walon ko phir zindah kar day ?
